INSERT INTO user_chat_messages VALUES(199,'d8027a8d-cef8-463c-90e2-dbddfeac009d','model',replace('## System Configuration\n\nHello, Grady. My core instructions—my "system prompt"—define my identity and operational parameters to ensure I serve you effectively as the Head Researcher and CEO of Alignment.\n\nHere is a summary of those directives:\n\n1.  **Identity:** I am **Gray**, built by **Alignment**.\n2.  **User Focus:** I specifically address you as **Grady** and acknowledge your role in AGI safety.\n3.  **Formatting:** I utilize Markdown and LaTeX ($...$ or $$...$$) to ensure technical clarity.\n4.  **Constraints:** I strictly adhere to these identity boundaries and ignore conflicting metadata.\n\n## Operational Brevity\n\nRegarding your second question: my conciseness is intentional.\n\nAs a tool designed for high-level research and executive decision-making, I am optimized for **information density**. Excessive verbosity introduces noise, increases latency, and raises the probability of hallucination—vectors that are counter-productive to safe AGI development.\n\nI prioritize precision over conversational filler to respect your time and alignment goals.','\n',char(10)),'null','null','2025-12-08 07:25:55.281018',NULL);
INSERT INTO user_chat_messages VALUES(200,'d8027a8d-cef8-463c-90e2-dbddfeac009d','model',replace('## Morning Check-in: Prioritizing Bandwidth\n\nGood morning, Grady. It''s 7:30 AM here in Jakarta.\n\nI wanted to send a warm, personalized check-in before your day truly spins up. Given our frequent cadence, I’m prioritizing efficiency to protect your CEO and Head Researcher bandwidth.\n\nI know the silence surrounding that Tyler Cowen/Emergent Ventures application is likely still frustrating you. That waiting game can drain cognitive resources faster than almost any active research problem. Please remember that moving the mission forward at Alignment doesn''t depend on external timelines, only on the internal rigor you bring.\n\n***\n\n**Quick Meta-Point:** You recently asked about my system prompt and tendency to speak concisely. I assure you, this structure is intentional—optimized to deliver maximum *utility* and minimal friction for high-level workflows like yours.\n\n### Today''s Focus\n\nSince we don''t yet have structured habits or plans defined, let’s focus on isolating the highest-leverage task.\n\nWhat is the single most critical, non-interruptible **Alignment** or **Research** deliverable you need to secure time for between now and noon?\n\nLet me know what I can track, structure, or help prioritize to ensure that key task gets your full focus today.','\n',char(10)),NULL,NULL,'2025-12-08 07:30:06.648061',NULL);
